<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>A sure fire destruction of +PvP</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Gray Rage (DB)">Gray Rage (DB)</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 6:46 a.m. 28/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> A sure fire destruction of +PvP<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>In my humble *grins* experience, I have seen a dramatic increase in chaos and plain destruction of a game by a lack of monster spawning.

<P>On the +PvP server there are usually few people and ALOT of monster which encourages cooperation amongst the players and a buffer against all out murder and lamer slayings (IE killin a guy with 10hps left after his battle with a nasty white monster). Now let's take away the monsters......MAYHEM. Surely there will be all kinds of nastiness goin on.
<P>Bottom line: make sure the monster population is HEAVY.
<P>-Gray
<P>THE FOLLOWING IS A CLASSIFIED ADVERTISEMENT:
<P>Are you plagued by a group of bandits on your merchant caravan? Has your sister been takin' by a Northern Barbarian tribe? Is your Keep set upon by the local Earl who thinks the lands should be his? Is a warrior out to get your trading guild by extorting 'protection' from you? Then you need the Mercenary Soldiers of <a href="http://personal.lig.bellsouth.net/lig/g/r/grayrage/dbmain.htm">DarkenBane Company!</a>
<P>The soldiers are highly capable and trained instruments of DEATH! If you have need of some muscle to straighten some things out just get down to the bank and then CALL <a href="http://personal.lig.bellsouth.net/lig/g/r/grayrage/dbmain.htm">DarkenBane Company</a>
<P>Legal Notice:
<P>DarkenBAne Comapny is a member of the High Order Dark Elven council. All payments must be made in advance in HARD currency (GOLD). Any termination of contract forfeits the advance fee. Member FCEI.
